{"tid":1288983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"災後心理輔導協會（PCCN) - 心理學家批：誤診","createTime":"2019-07-06T01:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T01:21:34.000Z","uid":266410,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5c34b36046590912cd6d35f7e0f5e6b89da905a9","tid":1288983,"uid":266410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T01:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/woEo30a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwoEo30a.png&h=545a51fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_679790_0?fbclid=IwAR2XsqSOvFaHA_c_CmvVBEwFGC5FkfsAZqxfDM3mi2v3FZbTep7xrMxf35Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_679790_0%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2XsqSOvFaHA_c_CmvVBEwFGC5FkfsAZqxfDM3mi2v3FZbTep7xrMxf35Y&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=a1a66853\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_679790_0%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2XsqSOvFaHA_c_CmvVBEwFGC5FkfsAZqxfDM3mi2v3FZbTep7xrMxf35Y&h=6944dfe9\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_679790_0?fbclid=IwAR2XsqSOvFaHA_c_CmvVBEwFGC5FkfsAZqxfDM3mi2v3FZbTep7xrMxf35Y</a><br />\n<br />\n網民擔心資料被盜<br />\n不少網民開始質疑PCCN的背景，指機構曾多次接受親中媒體訪問，擔心求助者個人資料會遭外洩。柳俊江和森美都已經將救心熱線宣傳帖文刪除，亦有媒體將杜永政訪問下架。記者到機構「接受治療」，發現中心內有清楚標示該處設有24小時閉路電視，但輔導室內的閉路電視附近就沒有任何標示。<br />\n<br />\n治療開始前輔導員遞給記者一份表格，索取資料包括中英文全名、身分證號碼、出生日期、性別、聯絡電話、電郵、通訊地址及教育程度。不過記者漏空「身分證號碼」一項，職員亦沒有要求記者填寫。<br />\n<br />\n表格寫明逃犯條例有關的心理輔導服務費用全免、談話內容絕對保密、輔導過程會被錄影及錄音等，<span style=\"color: red;\">並聲明言談間有違反香港法律言行或動機，PCCN將會向警方舉報並毋需得到案主同意</span>。記者當時就此條款追問輔導員，輔導員解釋，只會在案主透露有殺人動機等極端情況下才會報警。<br />\n<br />\n朱嘉麗指，一般臨床心理學家做法是會清楚告訴案主個人資料的保存期限，並說明資料只供輔導員或心理學家使用，<span style=\"color: red;\">但PCCN的輔導員當日並無說明資料保存期限，表格上亦無寫明</span>。"},{"pid":"5919c33b67c1ae5fa75c6b1b4cfcc68738f050a8","tid":1288983,"uid":230730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T01:15:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7eafb02bb4bc838310c8c884fae657d6eedcbf73","tid":1288983,"uid":266410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T01:17:50.000Z","msg":"總之就小心揀機構啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376366cd7bd9c18662a2fc9b719d3974bc2427d5","tid":1288983,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T01:21:34.000Z","msg":"推"}]}